er Final\n|{{flagicon|PNG}} [[Toti City Dwellers F.C.|Toti City]]\n|colspan=3; style=\"text-align:center;\"|4\u20130\n|-\n|rowspan=\"1\"|Semi Final\n|{{flagicon|NCL|football}} [[AS Magenta]]\n|colspan=3; style=\"text-align:center;\"|1\u20132\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\"|[[2020 OFC Champions League|2020]]\n|rowspan=\"5\"|[[OFC Champions League]]\n|rowspan=\"3\"|Group Stage\n|{{flagicon|FIJ}} [[Ba F.C.|Ba]]\n| colspan=2; style=\"text-align:center;\"|6\u20130\n|rowspan=3; style=\"text-align:center;\"|1st\n|-\n|{{flagicon|TAH}} [[A.S. V\u00e9nus|V\u00e9nus]]\n| colspan=2; style=\"text-align:center;\"|1\u20130\n|-\n|{{flagicon|SAM}} [[Lupe o le Soaga]]\n| colspan=2; style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\u20130\n|-\n|}\n\n===FIFA Club World Cup===\n\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|- style=\"background:#efefef;\"\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Year\n! colspan=\"8\" | [[FIFA Club World Cup]]\n! colspan=\"2\" | Top goalscorer\n! rowspan=\"2\" | Managers\n|-\n! Country.\n! Pl.\n! W\n! D\n! L\n! GS\n! GA\n! Place\n! \n! \n|-\n|align=center|[[2006 FIFA Club World Cup|2006]]\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''Japan'''\n|align=center|2\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|2\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|5\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''6th'''\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|{{flagicon|ENG}} [[Allan Jones (football coach)|Allan Jones]]\n|-\n|align=center|[[2009 FIFA Club World Cup|2009]]\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''UAE'''\n|align=center|3\n|align=center|2\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|5\n|align=center|5\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''5th'''\n|align=center|{{flagicon|NZL}} Jason Hayne\n|align=center|2\n|align=center|{{flagicon|NZL}} Paul Posa\n|-\n|align=center|[[2011 FIFA Club World Cup|2011]]\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''Japan'''\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|2\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''7th'''\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Ramon Tribulietx]]\n|-\n|align=center|[[2012 FIFA Club World Cup|2012]]\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''Japan'''\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|1\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''7th'''\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Ramon Tribulietx]]\n|-\n|align=center|[[2013 FIFA Club World Cup|2013]]\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''Morocco'''\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|2\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''7th'''\n|align=center|{{flagicon|FIJ}} [[Roy Krishna]]\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Ramon Tribulietx]]\n|-\n|align=center|[[2014 FIFA Club World Cup|2014]]\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''Morocco'''\n|align=center|4\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|2\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|3\n|align=center|3\n|style=\"text-align:center; background:bronze;\"|'''3rd'''\n|align=center|Three Players\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Ramon Tribulietx]]\n|-\n|align=center|[[2015 FIFA Club World Cup|2015]]\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''Japan'''\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|2\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''7th'''\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Ramon Tribulietx]]\n|-\n|align=center|[[2016 FIFA Club World Cup|2016]]\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''Japan'''\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|2\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''7th'''\n|align=center|{{flagicon|KOR}} [[Kim Dae-wook]]\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Ramon Tribulietx]]\n|-\n|align=center|[[2017 FIFA Club World Cup|2017]]\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''UAE'''\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|1\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|1\n|style=\"text-align:center\"|'''7th'''\n|align=center|-\n|align=center|0\n|align=center|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Ramon Tribulietx]]\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n\n===International===\n* '''[[FIFA Club World Cup]]'''\n::'''Bronze Medal''' (1): [[2014 FIFA Club World Cup#Final standings|2014]]\n'''Oceanian\n'''\n*'''[[OFC Champions League]]'''\n\n::'''Champions''' (9): [[2006 Oceania Club Championship|2006]], [[OFC Champions League 2008-09|2009]], [[OFC Champions League 2010-11|2011]], [[OFC Champions League 2011-12|2012]], [[OFC Champions League 2012-13|2013]], [[OFC Champions League 2013-14|2014]], [[OFC Champions League 2014-15|2015]], [[2016 OFC Champions League|2016]], [[2017 OFC Champions League|2017]]\n\n*'''[[OFC President's Cup]]'''\n::'''Champions''' (1): [[2014 OFC President's Cup#Final ranking|2014]]\n\n===National===\n*'''[[New Zealand Football Championship]]'''/'''[[ASB Premiership]]'''\n::'''Premiers''' (10): [[New Zealand Football Championship 2004\u201305|2004\u201305]], [[New Zealand Football Championship 2005\u201306|2005\u201306]], [[New Zealand Football Championship 2009\u201310|2009\u201310]], [[2011\u201312 ASB Premiership|2011\u201312]], [[2013\u201314 ASB Premiership|2013\u201314]], [[2014\u201315 ASB Premiership|2014\u201315]], [[2015\u201316 ASB Premiership|2015\u201316]], [[2016\u201317 ASB Premiership|2016\u201317]], [[2017-18 New Zealand Football Championship|2017\u201318]], [[2018-19 New Zealand Football Championship|2018\u201319]]\n::'''Champions''' (7): [[New Zealand Football Championship 2004\u201305|2005]], [[New Zealand Football Championship 2005\u201306|2006]], [[New Zealand Football Championship 2006\u201307|2007]], [[New Zealand Football Championship 2008\u201309|2009]], [[2013\u201314 ASB Premiership|2014]], [[2014\u201315 ASB Premiership|2015]], [[2017\u201318 New Zealand Football Championship|2018]]\n\n*'''[[Charity Cup|ASB Charity Cup]]'''\n::'''Champions''' (5): 2011\u201312, 2013\u201314, 2015\u201316, 2016\u201317, 2018\u201319\n\n*'''[[National Youth League (New Zealand)|National Youth League]]'''\n::'''Champions''' (5