lippines===\nList of exhibitors in the Philippines Pavilion:\n* 1964 \u2014 [[Jose Joya]]\n* 2015 \u2014 Manuel Conde, Carlos Francisco, Manny Montelibano, Jose Tence Ruiz (Curator: Patrick D. Flores)\n* 2017 \u2014 [[Manuel Ocampo]], [[Lani Maestro]] (Curator: Joselina Cruz)<ref>Maximil\u00edano Dur\u00f3n (October 13, 2016), [http://www.artnews.com/2016/10/13/manuel-ocampo-and-lani-maestro-will-represent-the-philippines-at-the-2017-venice-biennale/ Manuel Ocampo and Lani Maestro Will Represent the Philippines at the 2017 Venice Biennale] ''[[ARTnews]]''.</ref>\n* 2019 \u2014 [[Mark Justiniani]] (Curator: Tessa Maria Guazon)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.artsy.net/article/artsy-editorial-venice-biennales-10-best-pavilions|title=The Venice Biennale\u2019s 10 Best Pavilions|first=Casey|last=Lesser|date=May 10, 2019|website=Artsy|accessdate=June 3, 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Portugal===\nIn 1997, Portugal announced plans to build its own pavilion;<ref name=\"auto2\"/> these have not materialized since. \n\nList of exhibitors:\n* 1997 \u2013 [[Juli\u00e3o Sarmento]]<ref name=\"auto2\"/>\n* 2007 \u2013 \u00c2ngela Ferreira\n* 2011 \u2013 [[Francisco Tropa]] (Curator: Sergio Mah)\n* 2013 \u2013 [[Joana Vasconcelos]] (Curator: Miguel Amado)\n* 2015 \u2013 Jo\u00e3o Louro (Curator: Mar\u00eda de Corral)\n* 2017 \u2014 Jos\u00e9 Pedro Croft (Curator: Jo\u00e3o Pinharanda)\n* 2019 \u2014 Leonor Antunes (Curator: Jo\u00e3o Ribas)<ref>Andrew Russeth (March 13, 2019), [http://www.artnews.com/2019/03/13/leonor-antunes-will-represent-portugal-at-2019-venice-biennale/ Leonor Antunes Will Represent Portugal at 2019 Venice Biennale] ''[[ARTnews]]''.</ref>\n\n===San Marino===\nList of exhibitors:<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/art/archive/54th-exhibition/national-participations/|title=La Biennale di Venezia \u2013 National Participations|website=www.labiennale.org|access-date=2016-03-05}}</ref>\n* 1982 \u2014 Gilberto Giovagnoli, Walter Gasperoni (curated by [[Achille Bonit